+/* SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0-or-later */
+/*
+ * Copyright (c) 2016 Intel Corporation
+ * Copyright (c) 2023 Dorian Stoll
+ *
+ * Linux driver for Intel Precise Touch & Stylus
